@startuml Theme Switch Activity
!theme plain

title Activity Diagram - Theme Switch

start

:User opens Settings;

:Click "Themes" menu;

:System displays available themes:
* Dark Mode (Default)
* Midnight Mode
* Light Mode;

:User selects desired theme;

:System loads Resource Dictionary
for selected theme;

note right
    **WPF Resource Dictionary**
    - Colors
    - Styles
    - Control Templates
    - Brushes
    - Animations
end note

:Apply theme to UI
(No restart needed);

fork
    :Update window styles;
fork again
    :Update control styles;
fork again
    :Update color scheme;
end fork

:Save preference to database;

:Display success message;

stop

note left
    **Real-time Theme Switch:**
    - Uses WPF merged dictionaries
    - Dynamic resource resolution
    - No application restart
    - Smooth animations
    - Preference persisted
end note

@enduml
